      "status": "todo",
      "title": "Preserve combobox diagnostics after semanticAction visible-ref resolution",
      "description": "Post-reload Grafana stress smoke on 2026-05-15 exposed a regression gap: semanticAction role=combobox name=Job resolved through current snapshot refs to click @e65, focused the Grafana Job combobox, but did not emit details.comboboxFocus or visible Combobox diagnostic. No-op scroll diagnostics were active in the same reloaded session, so this appears specific to losing the original semantic combobox target after visible-ref resolution. Preserve original semanticAction role/locator context for combobox diagnostics while keeping ordinary-click false-positive protections and explicit aria-expanded=false/no-visible-options requirements. Add regression coverage for semanticAction role=combobox name click that resolves through snapshot refs and still emits details.comboboxFocus when focused closed combobox evidence qualifies. Update docs/contracts if trigger wording changes.",
